*Sreće* je ono što čini život zanimljivim. (Happiness is what makes life interesting.)

Život je pun *sreće*, ali i poteškoća. (Life is full of happiness, but also difficulties.)

Svi žele da žive u *sreći*. (Everyone wants to live in happiness.)

U današnje vreme, mnogi ljudi traže *sreću* u materijalnom dobru. (In today's world, many people seek happiness in material goods.)

Ne postoji ništa što može da zameni *sreću*. (There is nothing that can replace happiness.)